9,imgsize-463361.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[In 2000, an amateur explorer found a hidden cave in France filled with ancient art and burials]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131243139.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A hidden cave in France's Dordogne region, Cussac Cave, revealed thousands of years of history when explorer Marc Delluc discovered detailed Upper Palaeolithic art.  Further exploration uncovered an intact human skeleton, suggesting the cave served as a prehistoric burial site and a place of worship.  Remarkably, ancient footprints preserved in the mud indicate the use of sophisticated footwear.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2000-an-amateur-explorer-found-a-hidden-cave-in-france-filled-with-ancient-art-and-burials/articleshow/131243139.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2000-an-amateur-explorer-found-a-hidden-cave-in-france-filled-with-ancient-art-and-burials/articleshow/131243139.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T14:30:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131243770,imgsize-418404.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[In 2002, cavers found a hidden skeleton that revealed an ancient Australian predator]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131243130.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Explorers found an ancient marsupial lion skeleton in a Nullarbor Plain cave. This discovery offers a unique look at extinct life. The cave's stable environment preserved the fossil for millions of years. Researchers are studying the skeleton to understand the predator's strength and hunting abilities. This find reveals a hidden world beneath the desert surface.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2002-cavers-found-a-hidden-skeleton-that-revealed-an-ancient-australian-predator/articleshow/131243130.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/in-2002-cavers-found-a-hidden-skeleton-that-revealed-an-ancient-australian-predator/articleshow/131243130.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T14:08:04+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131243612,imgsize-114228.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[43-foot ‘marine T rex’ bigger than great white sharks and more brutal than any mosasaur discovered in Texas]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131259068.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/43-foot-marine-t-rex-bigger-than-great-white-sharks-and-more-brutal-than-any-mosasaur-discovered-in-texas/articleshow/131259068.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/43-foot-marine-t-rex-bigger-than-great-white-sharks-and-more-brutal-than-any-mosasaur-discovered-in-texas/articleshow/131259068.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T13:07:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131259188,imgsize-1534669.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Britain rolls out landmark transgender rules for single sex toilets, NHS wards and women-only spaces]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131258972.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Britain's new transgender access rules, following a Supreme Court ruling, allow single-sex spaces to exclude trans individuals if proportionate for privacy, safety, or dignity. This impacts healthcare, sports, and workplaces, sparking national debate on inclusion and rights. Organizations must balance protections, with case-by-case assessments encouraged.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-rolls-out-landmark-transgender-rules-for-single-sex-toilets-nhs-wards-and-women-only-spaces/articleshow/131258972.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/britain-rolls-out-landmark-transgender-rules-for-single-sex-toilets-nhs-wards-and-women-only-spaces/articleshow/131258972.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T13:18:28+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131259295,imgsize-94234.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[New anti-Hindu hate monitor launched in UK amid rise in religious hate crimes]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131258779.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/new-anti-hindu-hate-monitor-launched-in-uk-amid-rise-in-religious-hate-crimes/articleshow/131258779.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/new-anti-hindu-hate-monitor-launched-in-uk-amid-rise-in-religious-hate-crimes/articleshow/131258779.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T13:18:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131259366,imgsize-864010.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[China just installed a giant floating wind turbine and it could change the future of clean energy]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin