e><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131255020.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Amid escalating Iran tensions, President Trump expressed uncertainty about attending his son Donald Trump Jr.'s wedding this weekend in the Bahamas. He joked about facing criticism from the "fake news" regardless of his attendance, citing security concerns and the difficult timing due to international developments.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/if-i-do-attend-i-get-killed-donald-trump-says-he-has-a-thing-called-iran-stopping-him-from-attending-sons-wedding/articleshow/131255020.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/if-i-do-attend-i-get-killed-donald-trump-says-he-has-a-thing-called-iran-stopping-him-from-attending-sons-wedding/articleshow/131255020.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T08:05:29+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131255154,imgsize-1003128.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA["She is going to end up in jail again": Asmongold fires back after Nina Lin blames him for spending night in jail over $4 scissors]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131254289.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Asmongold responded harshly after Nina Lin blamed him and his viewers for a situation that allegedly led to her spending a night in jail over unscanned $4 scissors. During a livestream, Nina suggested an Asmongold viewer reported her to police. Asmongold mocked her claims, called the incident “stupid,” and predicted she would “end up in jail again,” escalating the viral feud across Twitch and social media platforms.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/she-is-going-to-end-up-in-jail-again-asmongold-fires-back-after-nina-lin-blames-him-for-spending-night-in-jail-over-4-scissors/articleshow/131254289.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/she-is-going-to-end-up-in-jail-again-asmongold-fires-back-after-nina-lin-blames-him-for-spending-night-in-jail-over-4-scissors/articleshow/131254289.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131254289,imgsize-41010.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Who is Maurice Shelmon aka Ant Jefe? No Jumper YouTuber and podcaster faces felony murder charge after LAPD arrest]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131251971.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Maurice Shelmon, also known as Ant Jefe, was reportedly arrested by the LAPD on a felony murder charge, according to TMZ. The No Jumper podcaster and rapper became known through YouTube videos, music, and podcast appearances. Following the arrest news, No Jumper hosts reacted during a livestream and expressed shock while speaking about his recent online success and growing platform.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-maurice-shelmon-aka-ant-jefe-no-jumper-youtuber-and-podcaster-faces-felony-murder-charge-after-lapd-arrest/articleshow/131251971.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/who-is-maurice-shelmon-aka-ant-jefe-no-jumper-youtuber-and-podcaster-faces-felony-murder-charge-after-lapd-arrest/articleshow/131251971.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T03:02:14+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131251971,imgsize-24124.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Judge orders ChudTheBuilder to wear GPS monitor and restrict social media use if released on bond]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131251913.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Controversial streamer Dalton Eatherly, known as ChudTheBuilder, faces stringent bail conditions following serious charges linked to a courthouse shooting. If released, he'll be electronically monitored via GPS, must surrender all weapons, and is banned from discussing the case publicly or on social media. These measures aim to ensure public safety and protect the ongoing legal proceedings.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/judge-orders-chudthebuilder-to-wear-gps-monitor-and-restrict-social-media-use-if-released-on-bond/articleshow/131251913.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/judge-orders-chudthebuilder-to-wear-gps-monitor-and-restrict-social-media-use-if-released-on-bond/articleshow/131251913.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T02:22:16+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131251922,imgsize-491014.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['At least 3 fewer Indians': Woman's post on Meta layoff affecting H-1B visa holder with wife and kid in Seattle draws flak]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131251877.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/at-least-3-fewer-indians-womans-post-on-meta-layoff-affecting-h-1b-visa-holder-with-wife-and-kid-in-seattle-draws-flak/articleshow/131251877.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/at-l