upporting her efforts and hoping for increased donations.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/81-year-old-minecraft-streamer-grammacrackers-swatted-during-cancer-fundraiser-stream/articleshow/131251666.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/81-year-old-minecraft-streamer-grammacrackers-swatted-during-cancer-fundraiser-stream/articleshow/131251666.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T01:13:27+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131251660,imgsize-712369.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Elon Musk agrees with what Jeff Bezos says on charity: 'If I do my job right...']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131251481.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-agrees-with-what-jeff-bezos-says-on-charity-if-i-do-my-job-right-/articleshow/131251481.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/elon-musk-agrees-with-what-jeff-bezos-says-on-charity-if-i-do-my-job-right-/articleshow/131251481.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T01:05:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131251524,imgsize-73202.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[China’s Moon base plans are pushing ahead faster than NASA’s lunar ambitions]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131251150.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/chinas-moon-base-plans-are-pushing-ahead-faster-than-nasas-lunar-ambition